title._content: Couple of guys standing in completed reservoir

description._content: Title: Standing in completed reservoir-0211201194311 Image Description: George Emken, Secretary and Peter Barendse, President of the Brownsmead Water District are standing in the completed reservoir. Photo was used in the Clatsop Annual Report for 1930, page 30. Original Collection: Extension Service Photographic Collection Item Number: P062:298 You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
